AddressInfo.Title: Rockford Supercharger
AddressInfo.AccessComments: From I-90/I-39 Southbound: Take the I-39 S/US-20/US-51 exit toward Rockford; Merge onto I-39 S/US-51 S;  Take exit 122A for Harrison Ave; Merge onto Harrison Ave; Turn right onto S Mall Dr; Turn left onto S Cherry Vale Mall Dr;  Station will be on the left.  /  From I-90 Northbound: Take the I-39 S/US-51 exit toward Rockford/US-20;  Merge onto I-39 S/US-51 S; Take exit 122A for Harrison Ave;  Merge onto Harrison Ave; Turn right onto S Mall Dr; Turn left onto S Cherry Vale Mall Dr;  Station will be on the left.  /  From I-39 Northbound: Take exit 122B for Harrison Ave; Merge onto US-20W; Continue onto Harrison Ave; Turn right onto S Mall Dr; Turn left onto S Cherry Vale Mall Dr; Station will be on the left.
